                Directions to the Office of Inspector General

                         National Science Foundation
                         Office of Inspector General
                      4201 Wilson Boulevard, Suite 1135
                          Arlington, Virginia 22230

   From Union Station by car or taxi
   (8 miles, 15 minutes)
     * Exiting Union Station, follow Louisiana Avenue, NW proceeding south
       to Constitution Avenue;
     * Turn right onto Constitution Avenue, NW;
     * Follow Constitution Avenue to signs for Route I-66 West, crossing
       the Theodore Roosevelt Bridge and staying in the left lane;
     * Exit I-66 West at Glebe Road, Exit 71/Route 120 (approximately 2
       miles);
     * Turn left at the end of the off ramp onto Glebe Road;
     * Proceed 1/2 mile (4 stop lights) to Wilson Boulevard;
     * Turn left onto Wilson Boulevard;
     * Turn left onto N. Stuart Street;
     * Turn right onto 9^th Street, NSF entrance is on the corner of
       Stuart and 9^th Street.

   From Ronald Reagan National Airport by car or taxi
   (6 miles, 15-20 minutes)
     * Stay in the left lane when exiting the airport terminal area;
     * Exit left following directions to Alexandria/Crystal City/Route 1
       and I-66; do not follow route to Washington, DC;
     * Follow signs to Alexandria, Route 1 South (Jefferson Davis
       Highway);
     * Turn right at second signal, on Route 120, S. Glebe Road;
     * Remain on Glebe Road for approximately 5 miles, passing under Route
       395 and subsequently passing by Ballston Common Shopping Center;
     * Turn right onto Wilson Boulevard;
     * Turn left onto N. Stuart Street;
     * Turn right onto 9^th Street; NSF entrance is on the corner of
       Stuart and 9^th Street.

   From Dulles Airport by car or taxi
   (21 miles, 25-30 minutes)
     * Stay to left on exiting airport area and join Dulles Access Road;
     * Follow signs to I-66 East and 495;
     * Continue to follow signs to I-66 East where the Access Road joins
       I-66 East, approx. 17 miles after leaving the airport;
     * Exit I-66 at Glebe Road;
     * Turn left at the end of off ramp onto Glebe Road;
     * Proceed 1/2 mile (4 stop lights) to Wilson Boulevard;
     * Turn left onto Wilson Boulevard;
     * Turn left onto N. Stuart Street;
     * Turn right onto 9^th Street; NSF entrance is on the corner of
       Stuart and 9^th Street.

   From the Metro

   To view the Washington, D.C. Metrorail system, click here:
   http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/local/longterm/metro/front.htm

